OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople avoid drinking over 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flack of public toilets     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Older people say they are intentionally
OL,6, dehydrating themselves or not leaving  
OL,7, the house because of a lack of public  
OL,8, toilets.                               
OL,10,FWales Senior Forum said many toilets   
OL,11,Fhad shut or become less accessible     
OL,12,Fsince the Covid pandemic.              
OL,14,FIts chairman Gareth Parsons called on  
OL,15,Fthe Welsh government to provide        
OL,16,Fspecific funding for public loos.      
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said it has       
OL,19,Fintroduced legislation to improve      
OL,20,Fpublic toilet accessibility.           
